Class PQRS

java.lang.Object
edu.uptc.Entidades.PQRS
Direct Known Subclasses:
Peticion, Queja, Reclamo, Sugerencia
public abstract class PQRS extends Object
Abstract base class representing a PQRS (Petition, Complaint, Claim, Suggestion) in the system. Contains common attributes for all PQRS types including registration date, description, and associated plan. Subclasses must implement the obtenerTipo method to specify the PQRS type.
